\p 
\v 17 “\w Then|strong="H1696"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w said|strong="H1696"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* Aaron \w and|strong="H4872"\w* \w Moses|strong="H4872"\w*/\w me|strong="H1696"\w*,
\v 18-20 “When the descendants of Kohath approach the sacred items in the Sacred Tent \add to take them to another location\add*, Aaron and his sons must always go in with them and show each of them what work to do and what things to carry. But the descendants of Kohath must not enter the Sacred Tent \add at any other time\add* and look at the things that are in it. If they do that, I will get rid of all the descendants of Kohath.”
\s1 The work of the men descended from Gershon
\p 
