\v 24 “\w This|strong="H2063"\w* \w is|strong="H4940"\w* \w the|strong="H5647"\w* \w work|strong="H5656"\w* \w that|strong="H4940"\w* \w they|strong="H5647"\w* must \w do|strong="H5647"\w* \w and|strong="H5647"\w* \w the|strong="H5647"\w* \w things|strong="H4853"\w* \w that|strong="H4940"\w* \w they|strong="H5647"\w* must \w carry|strong="H4853"\w* \add when you move to a new location\add*:
