\p 
\v 15 ‘When \w you|strong="H4886"\w* bring those animals, \w you|strong="H4886"\w* must also bring some wine \w to|strong="H4503"\w* offer \w as|strong="H5560"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w sacrifice|strong="H4503"\w*. \w And|strong="H8081"\w* \w you|strong="H4886"\w* must also bring \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w basket|strong="H5536"\w* \w of|strong="H4503"\w* \w bread|strong="H4682"\w* \w that|strong="H8081"\w* \w you|strong="H4886"\w* \w have|strong="H5262"\w* made \w with|strong="H1101"\w* very good \w flour|strong="H5560"\w* \w and|strong="H8081"\w* \add olive\add* \w oil|strong="H8081"\w*. But \w you|strong="H4886"\w* must not put any yeast \w in|strong="H4503"\w* \w the|strong="H4886"\w* \w bread|strong="H4682"\w*. Also brush/\w spread|strong="H4886"\w* some \add olive\add* \w oil|strong="H8081"\w* \w on|strong="H8081"\w* some thin \w wafers|strong="H7550"\w* \w and|strong="H8081"\w* bring \w them|strong="H4886"\w* \w to|strong="H4503"\w* \w the|strong="H4886"\w* priest.
