\c 11
\s1 Yahweh sent fire because the people complained
\p 
\v 1 \w One|strong="H1961"\w* day \w the|strong="H8085"\w* \w people|strong="H5971"\w* complained \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w about|strong="H1961"\w* \w their|strong="H3068"\w* \w troubles|strong="H7451"\w*. \w When|strong="H1961"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w heard|strong="H8085"\w* \w what|strong="H7451"\w* \w they|strong="H3068"\w* \w were|strong="H1961"\w* saying, \w he|strong="H3068"\w* \w became|strong="H1961"\w* \w angry|strong="H2734"\w*. \w So|strong="H1961"\w* \w he|strong="H3068"\w* \w sent|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* fire \w which|strong="H3068"\w* \w burned|strong="H2734"\w* \w among|strong="H5971"\w* \w the|strong="H8085"\w* \w people|strong="H5971"\w* \w at|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H8085"\w* \w edge|strong="H7097"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w their|strong="H3068"\w* \w camp|strong="H4264"\w*.
\v 2 \w Then|strong="H4872"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w people|strong="H5971"\w* \w cried|strong="H6817"\w* \w out|strong="H6817"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w Moses|strong="H4872"\w*/me, \w and|strong="H4872"\w* \w he|strong="H3068"\w*/\w I|strong="H3068"\w* \w prayed|strong="H6419"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w*. \w Then|strong="H4872"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* fire stopped burning.
\v 3 \w So|strong="H7121"\w* \w they|strong="H3588"\w* \w called|strong="H7121"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w place|strong="H4725"\w* \w Taberah|strong="H8404"\w*, \add which means ‘burning’\add*, \w because|strong="H3588"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* fire \w from|strong="H3068"\w* \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \w had|strong="H3068"\w* \w burned|strong="H1197"\w* \w among|strong="H8034"\w* \w them|strong="H7121"\w*.
\s1 Seventy leaders were chosen to help Moses
\p 
\v 4 \w Then|strong="H1571"\w* some troublemakers \w from|strong="H7725"\w* other people-groups \add who were traveling\add* \w with|strong="H7725"\w* \w the|strong="H7725"\w* Israelis \w began|strong="H3478"\w* \w to|strong="H7725"\w* want better food. \w And|strong="H1121"\w* \add when they started complaining\add* \w the|strong="H7725"\w* Israeli \w people|strong="H1121"\w* \w also|strong="H1571"\w* started \w to|strong="H7725"\w* \w complain|strong="H1058"\w*.
\v 5 \w They|strong="H2600"\w* said, “We wish \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w had|strong="H4714"\w* some meat!
\v 6 \w We|strong="H6258"\w* remember \w the|strong="H3605"\w* \w fish|strong="H5315"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* ate \w while|strong="H5315"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w were|strong="H5869"\w* \w in|strong="H5315"\w* Egypt, \w fish|strong="H5315"\w* \w that|strong="H3605"\w* \w was|strong="H5315"\w* given \w to|strong="H5315"\w* \w us|strong="H5315"\w* \w without|strong="H1115"\w* ◄cost/asking \w us|strong="H5315"\w* \w to|strong="H5315"\w* pay \w for|strong="H5315"\w* \w it|strong="H5315"\w*►. \w And|strong="H5869"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w had|strong="H5869"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* cucumbers, melons, leeks, onions, \w and|strong="H5869"\w* garlic \add that we wanted\add*. \w But|strong="H6258"\w* \w now|strong="H6258"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w do|strong="H5869"\w* \w not|strong="H1115"\w* \w have|strong="H5869"\w* \w any|strong="H3605"\w* \w desire|strong="H5315"\w* \w to|strong="H5315"\w* eat, \w because|strong="H3605"\w* \w all|strong="H3605"\w* \w we|strong="H3068"\w* \w have|strong="H5869"\w* \w to|strong="H5315"\w* eat \w is|strong="H5315"\w* \w this|strong="H6258"\w* \w manna|strong="H4478"\w*!”
\p 
