\v 33 \add Then they cooked them and started to eat them\add*. \w But|strong="H5221"\w* \w while|strong="H5750"\w* \w they|strong="H3068"\w* \w were|strong="H5971"\w* \w still|strong="H5750"\w* eating \w the|strong="H5221"\w* \w meat|strong="H1320"\w* [MTY], \w Yahweh|strong="H3068"\w* \add showed that he\add* \w was|strong="H3068"\w* \w very|strong="H3966"\w* \w angry|strong="H2734"\w* \w with|strong="H3068"\w* \w them|strong="H5221"\w*. \w He|strong="H3068"\w* \w struck|strong="H5221"\w* \w them|strong="H5221"\w* \w with|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H3068"\w* \w severe|strong="H7227"\w* \w plague|strong="H4347"\w*/sickness, \add and many people died\add*.
